{"tid":1399404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：英國《金融時報》回應解放軍鎮壓香港的傳聞。","createTime":"2019-08-03T07:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T12:31:52.000Z","uid":107060,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7bad619ecff976b4930adb8cc7b5ac07fd934a04","tid":1399404,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:03:46.000Z","msg":"陳雲：英國《金融時報》回應解放軍鎮壓香港的傳聞。中共向外舉債，75%在亞洲做，大部分舉債在香港做。香港沒有中共，會變回一個工商城邦，金融業務少了，但也減少高風險債務交易。中共沒有香港，馬上亡國。<br />\n&quot;In order to raise funding in US dollars, Chinese companies lean heavily on Hong Kong&rsquo;s financial markets &mdash; markets which are rooted in the city&rsquo;s independent legal system based on English Common Law....<br />\nIn debt capital markets, Chinese companies have borrowed $647bn in US dollar fundraising, or 75 per cent of all US dollars raised in Asia this year. Most of those debt deals are launched in Hong Kong.&quot;"},{"pid":"594f910c4aa39b6c97c96c1f45cc6d7dbdfd8e34","tid":1399404,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"Took medicine"},{"pid":"c8e1ede2f1ca6566db77acf674d4434d62022bcf","tid":1399404,"uid":250951,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d6311e1720fa0c427a4072428d89015d7caf11","tid":1399404,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:28:43.000Z","msg":"快！快點"},{"pid":"3ce0dd92a187c71038eb907262e90af11d0200d0","tid":1399404,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:40:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c82609a73387958c79d8b6d997fe355ed1daba","tid":1399404,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T10:39:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f06aa9eb447b789aa61e0d21cf295cde93226b63","tid":1399404,"uid":107060,"